 8, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Umm Habibah and Umm Salamah mentioned a church they saw in Abyssinia that had graven images in it. They mentioned it to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cVerily, when a righteous man among them would die, they would build a place of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14179,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/13\/malaikah-surah-tamathil-kalb\/","url_meta":{"origin":7649,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Images: Angels do not enter homes with dogs, graven images","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Talhah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe angels do not enter a house in which there is a dog, nor an image in a likeness.\u201d Abu Talhah said, \u201cThe Prophet means by likeness an image of living souls.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3225, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11050,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/khalq-graven-images-idolatry\/","url_meta":{"origin":7649,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: Folly of trying to rival Allah&#8217;s creation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: Who is mor